msgid "Second-Order"
msgstr "二階"

msgid ""
"The model could not be estimated. Ensure that factors have at least 2 "
"observed variables."
msgstr "模型無法估計。請確認每個因素至少要有兩個觀察變數。"

msgid ""
"The model could not be estimated. A factor with less than 2 variables was "
"added in Second-Order."
msgstr "模型無法估計。有個少於兩個變項的因素被設為二階因素。"

msgid ""
"Not more cases than number of variables. Is your data a variance-covariance "
"matrix?"
msgstr "資料個數少於變項個數，你是以變異數-共變數矩陣為資料進行分析嗎？"

msgid "FIML missing data handling only available with ML-type estimators"
msgstr ""
"只有使用最大概似法 (ML)類的估計法時，才能使用完全訊息最大概似法的方式來處理遺"
"漏值"

msgid ""
"Robust standard errors are not available with the GLS estimator. Try "
"changing the standard error method in the 'Advanced' settings to fit the "
"model."
msgstr ""
"以GLS估計法分析時，不提供穩健標準誤估計值。請在「進階」設定中修改標準誤方法之"
"設定。"

msgid ""
"Missing data handling '%s' is not supported for categorical data. \n"
" Please select another method under 'Missing data handling' within the "
"'Advanced' options tab"
msgstr ""
"遺漏值資料處理方式 '%s'不適用於類別資料\n"
"請在「進階」選項中的「處理遺漏值資料」中選擇其他的處理方法"

