msgid ""
"Fit statistics for each model. AIC and BIC penalize the log-likelihood for "
"model complexity and can be used to compare models with different numbers of "
"classes (lower is better). G² is the likelihood-ratio goodness-of-fit "
"statistic; a non-significant p-value indicates adequate fit, though this "
"test is sensitive to sparse cells and small samples."
msgstr ""
"各模型的適配統計量。AIC 與 BIC 會對模型複雜度下的對數概似值（log-likelihood）"
"進行懲罰，可用於比較不同類別數的模型（數值愈小愈佳）。G² 為概似比適配度統計量"
"（likelihood-ratio goodness-of-fit statistic）；其 p 值若未達顯著，表示模型具"
"有適當的適配度，但此檢定對稀疏儲存格（sparse cells）及小樣本相當敏感。"

msgid "Classes"
msgstr "類別數"

msgid "G²"
msgstr ""

msgid "N"
msgstr ""

msgid "%d Classes"
msgstr "%d 個類別"

#, fuzzy
msgid "Class Prevalences"
msgstr "類別盛行率"

msgid ""
"Estimated sizes of the latent classes. Proportion is the model-estimated "
"mixing weight (the probability that a randomly drawn observation belongs to "
"each class), with its standard error. Modal proportion is the fraction of "
"observations assigned to each class by their highest posterior probability; "
"it may differ from the model proportion because modal assignment discretizes "
"the continuous posterior."
msgstr ""
"潛在類別的估計規模。Proportion（比例）為模型估計之混合權重（即隨機抽取一筆觀"
"測值屬於各類別的機率），並附其標準誤。Modal proportion（眾數比例）則為依最大"
"後驗機率指派後，各類別所分配到的觀測比例；由於眾數指派將連續的後驗機率離散化"
"，因此其結果可能與模型比例不同。"

msgid "Class"
msgstr "類別"

msgid "Proportion"
msgstr "比例"

msgid "SE"
msgstr "標準誤"

msgid "Modal proportion"
msgstr "眾數比例"

msgid "Class %d"
msgstr "第 %d 類別"

msgid "Item-Response Probabilities"
msgstr "題項-反應機率"

msgid ""
"Estimated probability of each response category for each indicator, "
"conditional on class membership. Each row is a latent class; each column is "
"a response category of the indicator. Probabilities within a row sum to 1."
msgstr ""
"在各潛在類別條件下，每個指標之各反應類別的估計機率。每一列代表一個潛在類別；"
"每一欄代表該指標的一個反應類別。每一列內的機率總和為 1。"

msgid ""
"Grouped bar chart of item-response probabilities. Each panel shows one "
"latent class; bars within each panel show the probability of each response "
"category for every indicator. Taller bars indicate response categories more "
"characteristic of that class."
msgstr ""
"潛在類別之題項反應機率的分組長條圖。每個面板呈現一個潛在類別；每個面板內的長"
"條表示各指標之不同反應類別的機率分布。較高的長條代表該反應類別在該潛在類別中"
"較具代表性。"

msgid "Probability"
